Name: Description
COVID-19 Deaths by Age Group: Rates refer to the number of COVID-19 deaths, per 100,000 individuals in the age range.

Name: Source Notes
COVID-19 Deaths by Age Group:
New York City Department of Health and Mental Hygiene, COVID-19 Data (2020). Retrieved from: https://github.com/nychealth/coronavirus-data

Data for COVID-19 Deaths were updated weekly for the period of April 2, 2020 through April 2, 2021. These data are no longer being regularly updated. For the latest data on COVID-19, see: https://www1.nyc.gov/site/doh/covid/covid-19-data.page

Name: Notes
COVID-19 Deaths by Age Group: Data are cumulative and do not represent new deaths per day listed. Data are being collected in real-time and are preliminary and subject to change as COVID-19 response continues. Due to delays in reporting, recent data are incomplete.
